data.description: Don't miss this stunning, single story, 2150+ square foot home with attached RV garage in the sought after Surprise subdivision of Zanjero Trails!  Built in 2022 this energy efficient home boasts 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, 3 car tandem garage in addition to the 49 ft extended RV garage!  Tons of interior upgrades, including upgraded flooring, RO & water softener, dual pane windows, upgraded lighting, ceiling fans & fixtures, quartz countertops and upgraded kitchen w/ island, ss appliances, shaker cabinets, recessed lighting & pantry!  Primary suite with custom Barn Door, ensuite bath w/ dual links, spacious shower enclosure & walk in closet!  Finished backyard with brand new 23,000 gallon, heated pebble tech pool w/ waterfall & slide, turf & landscaping! Community park, walking paths, children's play area, sand volleyball and more!
